'''Soo Curlers Association''' is a curling club located in [[Sault Ste. Marie, Ontario]]. The curling club has been a registered club since 1944. Today the club is home to the reigning Olympic gold medalists Team [[Brad Jacobs (curler)|Brad Jacobs]].

The club plays at the '''Community First Curling Centre''', which was given its name in 2015 after being sponsored by Community First Credit Union.<ref>https://www.communityfirst-cu.com/SharedContent/documents/PressReleases/Community-First-Curling-Centre-Press-Release.pdf</ref>

